      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 09:37:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Altice France，交易中的债权人，可以使Drahi保持控制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/altice-france-strikes-creditor-deal-to-cut-8-6-billion-debt</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Altice France SA及其大多数债权人达成了一项协议，将公司的债务削减86亿欧元（90亿美元），让创始人Patrick Drahi保持对他多年收购建立的有线电视和移动电话运营商的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/altice-france-strikes-creditor-deal-to-cut-8-6-billion-debt</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 08:35:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国将至少550亿美元的新资本注入几家大银行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/china-plans-to-start-bank-capital-hike-with-at-least-55-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉此事的人们称，中国计划在未来几个月内重新注射其最大的三家银行，然后遵循去年揭幕的广泛刺激套餐，以提高经济困难的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-26/china-plans-to-start-bank-capital-hike-with-at-least-55-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Feb 2025 07:29:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
